using to illegally copy DVDs.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.350
This annoyed the internet.

00:03:52.350 --> 00:03:54.700
Ah, the internet-- this
annoyed them.

00:03:54.700 --> 00:03:57.850
So then they started to
taunt these people.

00:03:57.850 --> 00:03:59.430
So what they started
